* Pull Requests (PR)
** Purpose
***_ Code review before merging
***_ Catch issues collaboratively
** PR Workflow
***_ Clone → create branch → modify
***_ Commit & push to remote
***_ Open PR in Git provider
***_ Review & address feedback
***_ Merge into deployment branch
** Git Providers
***_ GitHub, Azure DevOps
***_ GitLab, Bitbucket
** Best Practice
***_ Each developer: own branch
***_ Sync local workspace after merge
@endmindmap
